==============
About JInvoice
==============

JInvoice is a desktop application for managing the daily collection and transactions of a small firm. User can create new clients or update the data, also could see the summary of all the invoices together. It is implemented in Java and uses MySql as a database for storing the invoices.

===========
Compilation
===========
$javac JInvoice.java

=========
Execution
=========
$java JInvoice

=====
Usage
=====
 - Executing the program opens a small login window so that only the invoice manager could see/add/update the invoices.
 - After that, the main app window will open on which user can add/update clients/invoices or could see the summarized collection of his firm.
